nt solution for businesses of all sizes its capabilities include content management document management knowledge management and others the software was designed and launched by epazz inc headquartered in illinois united states boxesos average rating this software product is not yet rated boxesos typical customerscustomers of the software include businesses of all sizes and types it has been deployed in a wide range of major industries some of which include financial services education legal services retail and wholesale healthcare and hospitality government automation and manufacturing business process outsourcing transport media and entertainment and othersboxesos featuresthe content management module of the software aims at providing secure management organization sharing and archiving of the enterprise content quarterly reports can be presented to stakeholders and other important data can be shared over secure links remote document access and management is offered for efficient workflow and content can be shared via multiple channels including websites emails rss feed and others boxesos offers website management for both public and private websites email content management is offered along with email templates which can be customized other important services of the software include poll management content aggregator customized reporting file management active directory integration prospect client management recruiting assessment management and others boxesos alternativespopular alternatives to boxesos  boxesos pricing informationthe price varies according to the business and team size license for small and medium organizations begins from  for active user under  for large organizations the price begins at  for over  active users epazz inc   software products  boxesos software by epazz inc updated may   boxesos is a learning management solution for businesses of all sizes its capabilities include content management document management knowledge management and oth