eller initiatives finland has been added to the growing number of markets in which epazz inc is now open for business having added others in asia and south america epazz inc with a focus on its fully owned subsidiary deskflex inc room scheduling software has entered into a new partnership to cover more of the market in europe the new distribution channel is through moonsoft a finnish company which specializes in software sales for small and medium size businesses academic institutions and the public sector including governmental institutionsmoonsoft in espoo finland has positioned itself as the company best able to assist customers to make an informed decision when it comes to selecting the right products and licensing for their needs moonsoft whilst having software sales at the foundation of its business has positioned itself as seller of the worlds leading software products in addition moonsoft also offers professional services support and tools to help its customers to properly manage the complete software lifecycle deskflex therefore has been added to moonsofts reliable and highly regarded lineupepazzs chairman and ceo shaun passley has indicated he is confident of the companys products capabilities which have been endorsed by the clients and the value they bring to them at this challenging time he also has confidence in his plans for continuing with expanding market presence we will look forward to our relationship with moonsoft we believe that moonsoft will also be a good reseller for autohire and intellisys said shaun passleyautohire is an applicant tracking system that competes favorably with other hiring system providers by providing a wide range of applicant tracking functionality combined with ease of use the system design is not complicated making it easy for the user to navigate quick access to candidates records is provided directly from the job postingsintellisys integrated plant management control ipmc is a hmi software system design for water and wastewater facility management ipmc is the technologybased strategy for optimizing operations by automatically collecting managing organizing and disseminating information for the operations management laboratory maintenance and engineering functionsabout epazz inc epazz inc is an enterprisewide software company that specializes in providing customized web applications to the corporate world higher education institutions and the public sector epazz inc has two fully owned subsidiaries in deskflex inc and professional resources management incepazz boxesosv is the complete business webbased software package for small to mid size businesses fortune  enterprises government agencies and higher education institutions boxesos provides many of the webbased applications organizations would have to buy separatelyboxesos allows for employees to view announcements online employees are able to share documents from multiple locations throughout the world with boxesos employees are able to take training courses and their supervisors are able to view the results online companies are able to create selfservice portals for their customers to pay for their invoice and download instructions companies can also create selfservice portals for their partners to request new marketing materials or view a demo boxesos connects to companies databases to easily bring all of their information togetherboxesos includes an intranet software portal extranet central knowledge repository document management workflow engine website management web collaboration email system and learning management system into one complete webbased solution which connects to organizations backend systemsboxesos allows the organization to startup by implementing elegant webenabled information dashboards for each stakeholder group functionality with administrative systems can be swiftly completed using boxesos connectors to other backend systems business applications that require upgrading can be upgraded on a prioritized ba